{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/people/bethany-shinkins","content_id":"b431cbc0-6772-48dd-8574-fadc4a490f6a","description":"Professor Bethany Shinkins is a Professor of Health Economics at Warwick Medical School at the University of Warwick. Bethany has a longstanding interest in screening and is a test expert member of the UK National Screening Committee. She is a co-investigator on the Yorkshire Lung Screening Trial, a randomised controlled trial to evaluate community-based low-dose CT screening for lung cancer, and iDx-LUNG which is a biomarker study embedded within the Lung Health Check.","details":{"body":"<p>Professor Bethany Shinkins is a Professor of Health Economics at Warwick Medical School at the University of Warwick.</p>\n\n<p>Bethany has a longstanding interest in screening and is a test expert member of the UK National Screening Committee. She is a co-investigator on the Yorkshire Lung Screening Trial, a randomised controlled trial to evaluate community-based low-dose CT screening for lung cancer, and iDx-LUNG which is a biomarker study embedded within the Lung Health Check.</p>\n","full_name":"Prof Bethany Shinkins","image":{"alt_text":"Prof Bethany Shinkins","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/62a72b528fa8f5039107d674/s465_Bethany_Shinkins__LIHS_Headshots_0P6A1370__002_.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","first_published_at":"2022-06-13T13:17:55+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/bethany-shinkins","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/bethany-shinkins","base_path":"/government/people/bethany-shinkins","content_id":"b431cbc0-6772-48dd-8574-fadc4a490f6a","document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-03-27T10:34:42Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Prof Bethany Shinkins","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/bethany-shinkins","withdrawn":false}],"role_appointments":[{"content_id":